title: KenKarta: Battle of the Onoxmon
description: In KenKarta, all are expected to develop their Gifts. But to stand against an army from the edge of the Abyss, cheetatarah, equidae, stable boy and Princesses alike must now rely on their Gifts to survive. Get ready. With the help of her daughters, this author has created a spectacular fantasy world where-in tweens and teens will revel.
author: Alison Kartevold
